docs.text: py_tenma_app python 🐍 flask application for tenma power supply. Acknowledgements I want to thank plants 🎋 for providing me oxygen each day. Also, I want to thank the sun 🌄 for providing more than half of their nourishment free of charge. Prerequisites Python(>=3.6) Installation execute below script for creating virtual environment and installing dependencies .\scripts\install_dependencies.bat Start App execute below script to start python flask application .\scripts\run_app.bat open running application in browser using the url displayed in "run_app.bat"
